rananisarSB51214 Super AI Toolbox is a lightweight yet extensible automation framework built for Chromium-based environments and AI-assisted workflows.
It acts as a multi-layer toolkit combining:
Browser automation (Chrome Extension MV3 architecture)
Content scripting for real-time page interaction
Background service worker logic for persistent state handling
Modular JavaScript components for rapid feature expansion
⚙️ Core Capabilities
🔁 Background task execution via service worker
🌐 DOM-level interaction using content scripts
🧩 Popup-based control panel UI
💾 Local state persistence using Chrome storage API
🔌 Ready for API / AI integration (OpenAI, Claude, Firebase, etc.)
🧠 Scalable architecture for future automation modules
🏗️ System Design Philosophy
Modular-first architecture → every feature is plug-and-play
Event-driven execution model → lightweight and reactive
Extension-native automation layer → no external dependencies required
AI-ready design → built for future intelligent agents integration
